version_description: Full song with intro and bridge.
For the intro: Pluck the A and B strings, then D-G-D-G. Do this twice for Am, Em, Fmaj7. For C and E7: pluck the A and B strings, then D-G-D for both chords.
For the into: pluck the A and B strings at the same time, then G-B-G-B, repeat this twice for Am, Em, and Fmaj7. Do it once for C and E7 each.
This version has the right chords throughout the whole song at a right timing, including the instrumental part at the pre-end of the song.
its got a better intro and the correct key
This is the chords to Sia's new single 'Free Me' which promotes HIV/AIDS awareness.
Added capo to simplify playing, corrected chord alignment over lyrics.
This version is the official remix with David Guetta and Afrojack.

song_name: The Day That You Moved On
